---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Logo from '../layouts/Logo.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About" description="Katsuhiro Yamakawa について">
  <section>
    <h1 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">About</h1>

    <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-zinc-700 dark:text-poi-focus/90 leading-relaxed">
      <p>ここに自己紹介が入ります。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Identity Architecture — サイトロゴの設計思想 -->
  <section class="mt-20 border-t border-zinc-200 pt-10 dark:border-zinc-700/40">
    <h2 class="mb-8 text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">Identity Architecture</h2>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-stretch">
      <!-- Logo preview -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-zinc-100/50 p-8 dark:bg-zinc-900/30 sm:basis-1/3 group/logo">
        <Logo size={80} class="h-20 w-20 transition-transform duration-500 ease-out group-hover/logo:rotate-180 group-hover/logo:scale-110" />
      </div>

      <!-- SVG source -->
      <div class="relative min-w-0 sm:basis-2/3">
        <span class="absolute -top-3 left-4 z-10 bg-zinc-50 px-2 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500 dark:bg-poi-base dark:text-zinc-500">
          SVG Source
        </span>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-zinc-950 shadow-lg">
          <pre class="overflow-x-auto p-5 text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-poi-accent"><code>{`<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <path d="M22 12a1 1 0 0 1-10 0
           a1 1 0 0 0-10 0"
        stroke="#5de4c7" />
  <path d="M7 20.7a1 1 0 1 1 5-8.7
           a1 1 0 1 0 5-8.6"
        stroke="#d482ab" />
  <path d="M7 3.3a1 1 0 1 1 5 8.6
           a1 1 0 1 0 5 8.6"
        stroke="#89ddff" />
  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"
        stroke="#cdffb8" />
</svg>`}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">
      このロゴは静的な画像ではなく、幾何学的な座標データとしてプログラムされています。コードを直接描画エンジンに渡すことで、解像度に依存しない明晰な視覚言語を実現しています。
    </p>
  </section>
  <ContactForm turnstileSiteKey="" />
</MainLayout>
